WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.858
The Lord showed me an American flag, and the American flag was transformed into a hundred-dollar bill.

00:00:07.859 --> 00:00:20.516
The hundred-dollar bill was waving in the wind, and all of a sudden, it started to transform into some kind of digital code—almost like crypto code.

00:00:20.517 --> 00:00:31.524
The crypto was all moving and alive; it was all kind of like an internet math code, moving and moving.

00:00:31.525 --> 00:00:49.107
I said, "Lord, what is this?"and the Lord said, "The dollar is about to turn into a digital dollar."He said it will be worth half of what it's worth right now, so a hundred-dollar bill would be worth fifty dollars.

00:00:49.108 --> 00:01:02.813
He showed me the banks went bankrupt. All the money that was in the banks—every person that had money in there, no matter if you were really rich or if you were poor—whatever was in the banks, they seized it.

00:01:02.814 --> 00:01:18.671
All the money was now property of the bank somehow. I don't know how they did it, but all the loans that you have on your house and on your cars and everything, I saw that they would call it a debt jubilee.

00:01:18.672 --> 00:01:35.488
Because they couldn't foreclose and take everyone's houses and cars because of the dollar crashing, they just wiped it out and created a new platform; they created a new digital dollar with this.

00:01:35.489 --> 00:01:53.974
Then the Lord showed me lines of people standing at Target and Walmart trying to get food, but they weren't dressed in poverty-looking clothes; they still had nice clothes on. It happened so suddenly; it was like an overnight deal.

00:01:53.975 --> 00:02:08.500
People were in lines at Target and Walmart for a mile long because there were no products and there was no food; there was hardly anything in these stores, and people were waiting just to get whatever they could get.

00:02:08.501 --> 00:02:13.828
I could see them all in a single-file line, and it stretched forever.

00:02:13.829 --> 00:02:29.458
He showed me certain cryptocurrencies that would go up in value, he showed me certain things that would happen with gold and silver, and he showed me that for this year, he talked to me about the Euro.

00:02:29.459 --> 00:02:35.454
He told me the Euro would be in trouble because of what was going on with Europe and this war.

00:02:35.455 --> 00:02:45.413
That was one of the words that he gave me when I was praying about 2023; that was one of the first signs that this was all going to happen like dominoes.

00:02:45.414 --> 00:02:57.892
So I just simply wanted to come on and tell everybody: the things that are fixing to start to happen are very serious. I want to say this too—I mistime sometimes.

00:02:57.893 --> 00:03:07.859
Whenever I am seeing and I am praying and the Lord's showing me things that are coming, there is like a depth perception.

00:03:07.860 --> 00:03:14.451
Sometimes it comes really quick, and sometimes he is showing me years in advance, and I don't know.

00:03:14.452 --> 00:03:25.259
So I just have to keep praying over it. It's like this: in 2018, he showed me that there was something going to happen with the chickens.

00:03:25.260 --> 00:03:31.828
He said the chickens were going to become very expensive and that the eggs were going to become hard to get.

00:03:31.829 --> 00:03:38.145
It would be very expensive for some eggs compared to what they usually were.

00:03:38.146 --> 00:03:52.318
So I ran out and bought 20 chickens, trying to make sure that I had enough chickens because of what he told me, acting on the word that he gave me, and that was in 2018.

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:56.747
So all the years went by and nothing happened. The next year went by, and nothing.

00:03:56.748 --> 00:04:02.373
And here we are; it went all the way through the pandemic, and nothing.

00:04:02.374 --> 00:04:06.719
I thought, "Man, I really had missed this; this is really flaky."I felt bad.

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:13.974
I had to apologize to my wife and I said, "I'm sorry, honey, I missed it."I bought all those chickens, and the Lord showed me.

00:04:13.975 --> 00:04:22.305
I guess that was averted; we prayed it away or something. And then here it is, 2023, and all the stuff about chickens.

00:04:22.306 --> 00:04:31.559
I believe we're just at the beginning of that. I believe there'll be more to it, maybe with the chickens.

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:38.304
Whatever the Lord shows me, like I said, sometimes it's four or five years before it manifests.

00:04:38.305 --> 00:04:48.580
That being said, I just wanted to let you all know that. Thank you.

